item.title: How Deep Is Your Love: A Tribute to the Gibb Brothers
item.description:
Friday, July 19, 2013, 7:30pm



Queensland Music Festival, Brisbane City Council, Network Ten and The Courier-Mail and The Sunday Mail present

HOW DEEP IS YOUR LOVE

Over two grand evenings, Australia's finest singers and musicians will gather to celebrate an extraordinary songbook.

More than a tribute concert, How Deep Is Your Love is a soulful homage to the Gibb brothers, whose vision and versatility transcends the ordinary and whose talents contributed to a musical legacy unparalleled in the history of pop.

Cost: Ticketed Event
Bookings: Tickets can be purchased from www.ticketmaster.com.au
Venue: Riverstage
Venue address: Riverstage, Gardens Point Road, Brisbane
Age: All Ages
